              '**Stack:** Python 3.10+, langchain, chromadb, openai, fastapi, uvicorn, pytest.',
              '**File layout:** `rag/ingest.py`, `rag/store.py`, `rag/chain.py`, `rag/api.py`, `rag/eval.py`, `web/index.html`.',
              '**Embedding model:** `text-embedding-3-small`. **Chat model:** `gpt-4o-mini`.',
              '**Chunking:** RecursiveCharacterTextSplitter(chunk_size=400, chunk_overlap=50); preserve filename + heading metadata.',
              '**Confidence:** map best similarity score (cosine) to a 0..1 score with a calibration constant.',
